name: Keynote Koala
description:
The Keynote Koala token allows you a premium seat at any of Gary’s public keynote appearances occuring during the time period from May 6, 2021 to May 5, 2024 with additional green room access to meet Gary at all such events (For example, if Gary does 13 public keynote appearances around the world you are able to use this token to attend all 13).

To activate this token after purchase there will be verification process on VeeFriends.com and there is no guarantee as to the number of public keynote appearances (if any) that Gary will make during the aforementioned time period. 

This token is verifiable for admission to VeeCon 2022, 2023, 2024

This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain

The Keynote Koala token allows you a premium seat at any of Gary’s public keynote appearances occuring during the time period from May 6, 2021 to May 5, 2024 with additional green room access to meet Gary at all such events (For example, if Gary does 13 public keynote appearances around the world you are able to use this token to attend all 13).

To activate this token after purchase there will be verification process on VeeFriends.com and there is no guarantee as to the number of public keynote appearances (if any) that Gary will make during the aforementioned time period. 

This token is verifiable for admission to VeeCon 2022, 2023, 2024

This token is a collectible that lives on the Ethereum blockchain
